Program: Omnibus
Title: Shoals of Capricorn
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376mln
Last Broadcast Date: 24 February 2003
A visit to Rodrigues, site of the RGS marine science research and education programme Club Mer. This continues the work of the Shoals of Capricorns investigating the remote Mascerene Plateau in the western Indian Ocean.